text: Raul de Senna (born 17 June 1983) is a Brazilian equestrian. He competed in two events at the 2004 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:Brazilian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Brazil Category:Equestrians at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:Pan American Games medalists in equestrian Category:Pan American Games bronze medalists for Brazil Category:Equestrians at the 2003 Pan American Games Category:Sportspeople from Belo Horizonte
